      "Roberson Design is seeking a motivated individual to manage and grow a flourishing young web department. Work directly with great clients and talented art director. Manage websites and other multimedia projects (CD ROM). Candidates must have at least 3 years of demonstrated web design/development experience, excellent communication and organization skills, and a self-directed and results-oriented mind set. Ideal candidate will also have graphic design skills and a working knowledge of Illustrator, Photoshop, Dreamweaver, Flash, FTP clients, workflow methodology and informational architecture (Mac OS). Competitive salary and benefits. EOE.\n\nContact Human Resources at:\n\n(202) 546-2260 - T\n\n(202) 546-0947 - F\n\ninfo@robersondesign.com\n\nAddress: 415 11th Street NE\n\nWashington DC 20002\n\nRoberson Design is looking for the very best talent in the visual\n\ncommunication field. If you are a highly motivated and creative\n\nindividual we are interested in knowing more about you.\n\nRoberson Design offers a fast paced studio environment,\n\nsmall but very rewarding, diverse, and challenging.",
