      "Lead Full Stack Software Engineer, Tech Lead 💰 Salary: $179,400 - 225,100 per year\n\nAt Capital One we are looking for a JavaScript engineer!\n\n🛠️ Our tech stack:\nAWS, Angular, Azure, Cloud, CSS, Docker, GCP, Support, Java, JavaScript, Kubernetes, NodeJS, NoSQL, Python, React, SQL, TypeScript, Web, microservices\n\n📝 Rquirements:\n- Bachelors Degree\n- Minimum of 4 years of experience in software engineering (internships do not count)\n- At least 1 year of experience with cloud computing (e.g., AWS, Microsoft Azure, Google Cloud)\n- Masters Degree (preferred)\n- Over 7 years of experience in one or more of the following: JavaScript, React, Angular, Node, Java, TypeScript\n- 3+ years of experience working with AWS, GCP, Microsoft Azure, or other cloud platforms\n- 4+ years of experience in open-source frameworks\n- At least 1 year of experience in people management\n- 2+ years of experience in Agile methodologies\n\n👩‍💻👨‍💻 Your responsibilities are:\n- Lead a range of technology projects and a team of developers skilled in distributed microservices and full stack architectures to create solutions for regulatory compliance\n- Engage in software development for web applications utilizing a test-driven approach\n- Share your enthusiasm for technology trends by experimenting with new solutions and mentoring fellow engineers\n- Collaborate with digital product managers to deliver effective cloud-based solutions that enable financial empowerment for millions\n- Employ programming languages such as JavaScript, Java, HTML/CSS, TypeScript, as well as frameworks like Angular and React, along with Express NodeJS, SQL, Python, Go, container orchestration tools including Docker and Kubernetes, and various AWS services\n\nView this job and over 500 other transparent jobs with salaries (💰💰💰) & tech stacks (🛠️) on DevITJobs\n\nCategory: JavaScript Developer / Engineer\nLocation address: North Capitol Street NW 732, Washington, D.C., United States\n\nSalary: $179,400 - 225,100 per year\n\nBenefits & perks that we offer:\n\nCapital One - More about us and the role:\nAt Capital One, we are innovators in technology, creating solutions that address real problems and meet customer needs. Our team is made up of dynamic individuals who are committed to collaboration and continuous improvement in a fast-paced environment. We offer a strong compensation package, including performance-based incentives, and comprehensive health and financial benefits. This position is available in McLean, VA and Wilmington, DE, with competitive salaries ranging from $179,400 to $225,100, depending on location. We embrace diversity and are an equal opportunity employer, ensuring a work environment free from discrimination.\n\nAre you looking for JavaScript jobs in Washington, D.C.?",
